Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the organization learned that\NShinichi and Conan were the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone close to me would be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who knows\Nthe truth is Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hide my identity yet again today,\Nin which there is only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan's Abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing\Nas "the perfect crime."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to say this, but your\Ncrime is as clear as daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made three very basic mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistake #1: Cans scattered around\Nthe waste bin in an unnatural fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of cans is proof enough\Nthat there's something inside the bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistake #2: The ice cream bar you\Nwere just eating is lying nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You were in a rush to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you dropped it on the ground,\Nhalf-eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistake #3: The most\Nincriminating evidence of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that I can see your big butt\Ninside the waste bin, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:35.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! I found Genta too! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun when you're it--\Nthe game always ends right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun for me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A high school student playing\Ndetective games in the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These badges are so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say "Detective Boys" since\Nwe're the Junior Detective Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only grade school students\Nin the world with badges like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tiny transceivers built inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can communicate over long distances
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by using the dial on the\Nback to change frequencies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for kids' games,\Nbut I'd rather not have to play myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they hadn't come over\Nto invite me to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've gone with Ran to\NTeitan University's school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry! I'll have plenty\Nof fun with the college girls for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! This time I'll be the detective\Nand you guys'll be the criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be a criminal again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only need one detective!\NNow get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hide-and-Go-Seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I keep\Ngoing along with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if this keeps up\Nand I turn stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy daisy. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,99, 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! Time to show you all\Nthe skill of Genta Kojima-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leader of the Junior Detective Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta's looking hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Multiple girls kidnapped and murdered."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't\Ncaught those guys yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute girls are the only ones\Nthey're going after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I'm in huge danger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something bad ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be there to protect me,\Nwouldn't you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're destined\Nto be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, Ayumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be good at finding people,\Nbut you sure suck at hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate running away\Nand hiding from people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird though, I could\Nswear I heard Ayumi's voice too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Hurry and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Somewhere for me to hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keepin' that idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd. Scientifically speaking,\Nhe shouldn't have found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was scientific about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That leaves just Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumb Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long can it possibly take him\Nto find an ordinary little girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not an ordinary little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll tune up the skateboard\Nthe professor gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you mind if I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you... How do you\Nfeel about Ayumi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you how you\Nfeel about her as a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As just a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko... Don't tell me you\Nhave a crush on Ayumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm simply asking your opinion\Nto help me decide on my "life plan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life plan? You're not talking\Nabout marriage, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky! The professor\Nmakes so much stuff for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so damn long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I already said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble if we don't get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't found Ayumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up and have her come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd ever say anything\Nthat uncool in front of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So Genta likes Ayumi-chan too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're destined\Nto be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a situation\NI've gotten myself into...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it quits.\NYou can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she went\Nhome without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the volume up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NSomewhere dark and cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hid in the trunk of a car\Nthat was stopped in front of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I got sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the park?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money! There's tons\Nof it in a paper bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A million yen times 100, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car must belong to someone rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would that much money\Nbe in a paper bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else\Nbesides the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there is. It looks\Nlike a plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it filled with\Ngrilled eel lunches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look, a saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A saw...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's this thing?\NIt's slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You been hearin'\Na kid's voice come from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. There's no way\Nthat thing could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the saw the only thing\Ninside the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also something round\Nand wrapped in paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see what's inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't open that, Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a head! A girl's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the car Ayumi-chan got in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,belonged to those kidnappers\Nwho're killing little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me check out the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, unlock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So that's what we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That had me scared for a minute there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Ayumi-chan!\NThey'll hear you if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Think of something funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered how\NGenta-kun looked like a bear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he fell down the stairs\Nthe other day and got two bumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:48.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls don't make sense,\Neven at times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan. You can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet and don't move a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are you gonna chase them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in a car, you know!\NIt'll be hopeless with that skateboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professor made this for me--\Nit's no ordinary skateboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's equipped with a\Nhigh-performance turbo engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's solar powered, so you can\Nonly use it when the sun is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hour until sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?\NYou guys wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That car belongs to\Na couple of murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder, schmurder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit here\Nwhile Ayumi-chan is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting women is a man's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Where's the car now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This car's weird, it keeps\Nmoving and then stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus there are weird sounds outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn up your badge's volume, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! They're stuck in traffic\Nbecause of road construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only place around here\Nwhere there's construction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is at the intersection on 2nd Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Better hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to kill her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents paid the ransom,\Nand besides, she's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! She's seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave her alive!\NEven if she is just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Ayumi! We're coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is their car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi! Are you still stopping and going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But it's not\Nthe same place as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear those\Nweird sounds anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plus the car just drove a long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. If they're in a\Ntraffic jam up ahead, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The freeway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! There's no catching them\Nif they get on the freeway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure have been a lot\Nof police cars passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the fourth one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the kidnappers appear to have\Nescaped to the city of Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The authorities have\Nformed a police cordon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are trying as hard\Nas possible to arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Have you\Nheard any police cars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! About 3 of them passed\Nby when we were stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!\NThey've set up an inspection checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably where the roads converge\Nright before the freeway starts--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on Beika Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Beika Bridge is straight\Ndown that last street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! They wouldn't dare\Ngo through the checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd obviously take a side street\Nto get out of Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without going over the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll have to come down this street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving! The car's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! You're as good as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?\NIt's already been 5 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the heck's going on, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Is the car stopped\Nright now? Or is it moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Ayumi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she go out of range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, these things have a\Nbroadcast radius of 20 kilometers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they could've\Ngone that far in 5 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's in a tunnel\Nor something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Tunnel! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they'd have to pass through the\Ninspection point and go over the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to enter Beika Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means they must be inside\Na building that disrupts our signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think it's\Ntheir hideout, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nthey're like rats in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police'll find them eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find Ayumi-chan\Nbefore they get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's seen our faces.\NWe can't leave her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she is just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something bad ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be there to protect me,\Nwouldn't you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...na... ku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't you say anything,\Nyou jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll hear you if you yell too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they would hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car's so loud that\NI can't hear their voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where you are right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There was this roaring sound\Nand then you stopped replying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roaring sound? So they\Nwere in the tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did they pass\Nthrough the checkpoint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come after you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep quiet and wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The skateboard'll stop\Nsoon if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! It sounds like the car's\Nin some sort of shop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard someone say, "Welcome,"\Nand this weird sound just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gas station! Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Let me hear\Nwhat's going on outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently giving away\NMasked Yaiba towels and T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any!\NWe're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only gas station you\Ncan get Masked Yaiba stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Yotsubishi Gas,\Nwhich we just passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound, Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan's definitely\Nin the trunk of that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As is the girl's head and the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones kidnapping\Nand killing little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear\Nanything strange just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some kids playing pranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Ayumi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan! Respond! Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something's definitely strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a stray cat.\NNo need to get worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! There's no escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! There's not enough solar power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something\Nbefore we stop altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop, you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car! Or else I'll do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just hurry! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! My hands are going numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold on any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi! Ayumi! Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Let's just get her\Nout of there and split!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had us worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who've been kidnapping\Nand murdering little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murdering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard your guys'\Nconversation in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You said you'd have\Nno trouble killing little kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's the corpse\Nand money in your trunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try talking your way out of that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a better look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all hand-made props!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Props?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our conversation in the car was us\Npracticing our lines one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practicing your lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're performing in a play here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Teitan University's\Nschool festival, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they're going to have\Nan interesting mystery play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, they said on the radio\Nthat they just caught the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So was that the real killer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a big lump and a broken neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was nice meeting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to take\Nresponsibility for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:56.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:05.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:10.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:17.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:26.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:34.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:40.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:50.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:55.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents paid the r... ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and besides, she's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! She's seen our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's something weird\Nabout that actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't stand up straight,\Nand he keeps blowing his lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so beautiful, Miss!\NWhat do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, now! Wouldn't you like\Nto see my famous detective skills--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta! Say the next line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:44.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to read this word!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right--we were put onstage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pronounced "cruel"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:50.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the role of \Nthe decapitated head...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...went to Ayumi-chan herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Hide-and-Go-Seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she just found her father, too!\NHow horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still no saying\Nfor sure that he was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.19,0:24:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Masami-san?\NWhat's happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bizarre Manhunt Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.10,0:24:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.04,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hundred Million Yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's mystery is another huge one.
